--- 1. whitespace control: {%- -%} strips both sides ---
abc
--- 2. left-only and right-only strip ---
[KEEP_RIGHT_WS]
--- 3. {{- -}} on outputs ---
xALICEy
--- 4. filter: upper / lower / capitalize ---
ALICE
alice
Alice
--- 5. filter: length ---
4
5
--- 6. filter: default ---
fallback
alice
--- 7. filter: trim / replace / truncate ---
[spaced]
aYbYc
hello...
--- 8. filter: join ---
a, b, c
--- 9. filter chain ---
@LICE
--- 10. filter: safe skips auto-escape ---
<b>bold</b>
--- 11. filter: escape forces escape on RAW ---
&lt;b&gt;bold&lt;/b&gt;
--- 12. custom filter via register_filter ---
hi!
--- 13. inheritance: child overrides title + body, inherits heading ---
<!doctype html>
<title>child title</title>
<body>
<h1>default heading</h1>
hello alice!
</body>

--- 14. inheritance: grandchild extends child extends base ---
<!doctype html>
<title>child title</title>
<body>
<h1>grandchild heading</h1>
hello bob!
</body>

